  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>End of the line. All passengers must disembark</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <i>The Last Train</i>, a first-person psychological horror game, routine turns into nightmare when you fall asleep on the subway. When you wake up, you’ve reached the end of the line — an abandoned station shrouded in darkness. But you’re not alone; something is waiting in the shadows, watching you, following your every move.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the dark hallways and hidden corners of the last station as you try to find a way back to safety. Every sound, every movement, could mean the thing chasing you is closer than you think. You'll need to stay calm, solve puzzles, and find clues that reveal the dark secrets hidden in this forgotten station.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Will you escape before the entity catches you?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >First-person horror with a touch of humor</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 endings to unlock</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A viral social media character is after you</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover secrets that reveal a greater story</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Intense experience in a mysterious station</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3676960/extras/802dc12bc62c77e10c133c44046af55b.poster.avif?t=1773087867\" width=960 height=540 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3676960/extras/802dc12bc62c77e10c133c44046af55b.webm?t=1773087867\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3676960/extras/802dc12bc62c77e10c133c44046af55b.mp4?t=1773087867\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Get ready for a one-way ride into fear. The last stop awaits… and not everyone makes it back.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3676960/extras/1c27faf1eac9fa8f067ffb4cf0b2b33d.poster.avif?t=1773087867\" width=960 height=540 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3676960/extras/1c27faf1eac9fa8f067ffb4cf0b2b33d.webm?t=1773087867\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3676960/extras/1c27faf1eac9fa8f067ffb4cf0b2b33d.mp4?t=1773087867\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>End of the line. All passengers must disembark</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <i>The Last Train</i>, a first-person psychological horror game, routine turns into nightmare when you fall asleep on the subway. When you wake up, you’ve reached the end of the line — an abandoned station shrouded in darkness. But you’re not alone; something is waiting in the shadows, watching you, following your every move.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the dark hallways and hidden corners of the last station as you try to find a way back to safety. Every sound, every movement, could mean the thing chasing you is closer than you think. You'll need to stay calm, solve puzzles, and find clues that reveal the dark secrets hidden in this forgotten station.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Will you escape before the entity catches you?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >First-person horror with a touch of humor</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 endings to unlock</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A viral social media character is after you</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover secrets that reveal a greater story</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Intense experience in a mysterious station</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3676960/extras/802dc12bc62c77e10c133c44046af55b.poster.avif?t=1773087867\" width=960 height=540 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3676960/extras/802dc12bc62c77e10c133c44046af55b.webm?t=1773087867\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3676960/extra